  "description": "<h1>Mexicali-Imperial Valley-Yuma</h1>\n<h3>MXL · 1.0.0</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Subway-Builder-Modded/registry/refs/heads/main/maps/mexicali/gallery/screenshot1.webp\" alt=\"Map Preview\"></p>\n<h2>Coverage</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Bounding box</strong></td><td>-115.70149, 32.17491, -114.37200, 33.26477</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Playable Area</strong></td><td>~15,000 km²</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Population Summary</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Total Modeled Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">801,423</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Modeled Normal Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">673,298</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Modeled Special Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">128,125</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Map Statistics</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Demand Points</strong></td><td align=\"right\">2689</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Populations</strong></td><td align=\"right\">17,416</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Special Demand</h2>\n<details>\n<summary>Airports — 2150</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;TIJ&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;16,800&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;SAN&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;34,400&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;CLD&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;950&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Borders — 38,000</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Andrade&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1200&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Calexico&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;16800&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Calexico East&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;8000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;San Luis&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;12000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Universities — 37,050</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Universidad Autónoma de Baja California&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;12600&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;CETYS Universidad&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1800&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Instituto Tecnológico de Mexicali&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;2000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Universidad Politécnica de Baja California&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;750&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Universidad Xochicalco&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;850&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Universidad del Valle de México&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;2100&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Universidad Tecnológica de San Luis Río Colorado&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;500&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;San Diego State University Imperial Valley-Calexico&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1100&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Imperial Valley College&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;8000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Arizona Western College&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;7000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;University of Arizona Yuma&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;350&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Entertainment — 41,825</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Bosque y Zoológico de la Ciudad&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1100&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Plaza Cachanilla&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;12200&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Catedral de Nuestra Señora de Guadalupe&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1100&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Centro Estatal de las Artes (CEART)&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;425&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Casino Golden Lion&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;900&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Arenia Casino&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1400&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Flyers Jump & Fun Mexicali&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;500&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Casino Prestige&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;825&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Museo Sol del Niño&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;300&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Parque Acuático Mellaya&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;225&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Estadio Nido de los Águilas&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;775&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Bosque de la Ciudad (SLRC)&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;825&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Ciudad Deportiva&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;4000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Parque Deportivo Necaxa&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1200&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Auditorio del Estado&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;400&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Unidad Deportiva Independencia&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;500&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Unidad Deportiva Baja California&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;675&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Unidad Deportiva Alamitos&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;275&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Imperial Sand Dunes&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;3200&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Imperial Valley Mall&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;5400&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Gran Plaza Outlets&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;3400&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Yuma County Fairgrounds&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1100&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Salvation Mountain&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;350&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Slab City&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;275&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Arizona Market Place&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;250&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Lutes Casino&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;225&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Military Bases — 9100</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Naval Air Facility El Centro&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1600&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Marine Corps Air Station Yuma&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;5200&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Yuma Proving Ground&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;2300&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n<br>\n\n<h2>Additional Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Building Collision</strong> — A buildings index is included, providing in-game collision geometry for all non-filtered buildings.</li>\n<li><strong>Neighborhood Labels</strong> — The map includes municipal and neighborhood labels derived from administrative boundary data.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Methodology</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>MX data:<ul>\n<li>Processed INEGI&#39;s DENUE, CE, CPV, and ITER data sets for the entire country.</li>\n<li>Estimated business job counts by taking the geometric means of strata.</li>\n<li>Aggregated businesses to the block level.</li>\n<li>Estimated uncounted/informal jobs via the ENOE data set.</li>\n<li>Extracted relevant points for the bounding box of this map, then applied a modified version of Colin&#39;s gravity model.</li>\n<li>Added special demand via the Demand Adder.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>US data:<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rslurry/subwaybuilder-US-demand-data\">subwaybuilder-US-demand-generator</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Border data:<ul>\n<li>Assumes 50% of crossing happen from US side, and 50% happen from MX side. Values rounded down to ensure an equal number of pops for both.  Commutes to/from the border point are separately done for MX and US sub-maps (where pops live/work at the border crossing and work/live somewhere in the city), then pops are paired up to form commutes from MX to US and vice versa.  A 30 minute border crossing time penalty is applied to the commute.  The Cross Border Xpress is exempt for this model, since it exists as a way for pops to enter/exit TIJ airport on the US side, and so the border crossing time does not impact the commute to/from CBX, and these pops do not have any origin/destination in MX.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Data Sources</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.inegi.org.mx/programas/ce/2024/\">INEGI Censos Económicos (CE) 2024</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.inegi.org.mx/app/mapa/denue/default.aspx\">INEGI Directorio Estadístico Nacional de Unidades Económicas (DENUE)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.inegi.org.mx/programas/ccpv/2020/\">INEGI Censo de Población y Vivienda (CPV) 2020</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.inegi.org.mx/app/descarga/ficha.html?tit=326108&ag=0&f=csv\">Principales resultados por localidad (ITER)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.inegi.org.mx/programas/enoe/15ymas/\">INEGI Encuesta Nacional de Ocupación y Empleo (ENOE)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://lehd.ces.census.gov/data/\">US Census Bureau LEHD Origin-Destination Employment Statistics (LODES)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://data.bts.gov/stories/s/jswi-2e7b\">US Bureau of Transportation Statistics Border Crossing/Entry Data</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>License</h2>\n<p>This map data is released under the <a href=\"https://github.com/rslurry/subwaybuilder-maps/blob/main/LICENSE\">GNU General Public License v3.0</a>.</p>\n<h2>Credits</h2>\n<p>Map authored by slurry</p>",
